  30:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) Enable the RTC domain access.
  31:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) Configure the RTC Prescaler (Asynchronous and Synchronous) and RTC hour
  32:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         format using the HAL_RTC_Init() function.
