 100:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****      (+) To write to the RTC Backup Data registers, use the HAL_RTCEx_BKUPWrite()
 101:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****          function.
 102:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****      (+) To read the RTC Backup Data registers, use the HAL_RTCEx_BKUPRead()
 103:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****          function.
 104:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****      (+) STM32L412xx and STM32L422xx only : Before calling these functions you have to call HAL_RTC
