 152:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @brief  Set TimeStamp.
 153:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @note   This API must be called before enabling the TimeStamp feature.
 154:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  hrtc RTC handle
 155:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  TimeStampEdge Specifies the pin edge on which the TimeStamp is
 156:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *         activated.
 157:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
 158:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_TIMESTAMPEDGE_RISING: the Time stamp event occurs on the
 159:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *                                        rising edge of the related pin.
 160:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_TIMESTAMPEDGE_FALLING: the Time stamp event occurs on the
 161:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *                                         falling edge of the related pin.
 162:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  RTC_TimeStampPin specifies the RTC TimeStamp Pin.
 163:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
 164:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_TIMESTAMPPIN_DEFAULT: PC13 is selected as RTC TimeStamp Pin.
 165:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *               The RTC TimeStamp Pin is per default PC13, but for reasons of
 166:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *               compatibility, this parameter is required.
 167:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @retval HAL status
 168:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   */
